about.description: This extension allows BibTeX citations to be inserted into documentation generated by Sphinx."
about.summary: A Sphinx extension for BibTeX style citations.

name: sphinxcontrib-bibtex
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "sphinxcontrib-bibtex" %}
{% set version = "0.4.2" %}
{% set hash_type = "sha256" %}
{% set hash_value = "169afb3a3485775e5473934a0fdff1780e8bdcdd44db7ed286044a074331c729" %}

package:
  name: '{{ name|lower }}'
  version: '{{ version }}'

source:
  fn: '{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz'
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  '{{ hash_type }}': '{{ hash_value }}'

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed .

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
    - setuptools
    - pybtex >=0.20
    - pybtex-docutils >=0.2.0
    - six >=1.4.1
    - sphinx >=1.6
    - oset >=0.1.3
  run:
    - python
    - pybtex >=0.20
    - pybtex-docutils >=0.2.0
    - six >=1.4.1
    - sphinx >=1.6
    - oset >=0.1.3

test:
  imports:
    - sphinxcontrib
    - sphinxcontrib.bibtex

about:
  home: https://github.com/mcmtroffaes/sphinxcontrib-bibtex
  license: BSD 2-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE.rst
  summary: A Sphinx extension for BibTeX style citations.
  description: This extension allows BibTeX citations to be inserted into documentation
               generated by Sphinx."
  doc_url: http://sphinxcontrib-bibtex.readthedocs.org/en/latest/
  dev_url: https://github.com/mcmtroffaes/sphinxcontrib-bibtex/

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - croth1
